    "description": "维维亚大陆上流传着古老的传说。<br><br>传说中大陆上各个种族的祖先是飞龙一族。<br><br>但是很久以前飞龙们就从大陆上消失了。。。<br><br>现在，整个大陆陷入了混乱，邪恶的怪物不停的入侵整片大陆。<br><br>而你将扮演一个新人佣兵，拜访各种各样的城镇，探索危险重重的地牢，不断变强。<br><br>保护大陆的同时，找到怪物入侵的真相，探索这个剑与魔法的世界，揭开飞龙消失的谜团，并解锁龙族血脉的力量！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/0bd1e8ae077182b5ccc93b4b49b14a7e.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/d96fe4da69de2e351e45491f9e4302b7.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/d96fe4da69de2e351e45491f9e4302b7.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/d96fe4da69de2e351e45491f9e4302b7.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏采用了非常简单的即时战斗系统，搭配上不同的武器和技能，可以让你轻松上手，充分体验到战斗的爽快和乐趣！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a9e52a7a04ab91aaa46eab202d7732dd.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a1ade34212cee67a8c2a864906f11dd8.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a1ade34212cee67a8c2a864906f11dd8.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a1ade34212cee67a8c2a864906f11dd8.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在试玩版游戏中一共有四个职业可以选择，你可以成为一个手握冷兵器的战士，也可以成为一个精通各种魔法的法师。此外，游戏的跨职业技能系统还允许你使用其他职业的技能，无论是近战法师还是魔剑士都可以实现！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/4f6f558ee67135f98cd06809daf1f205.avif?t=1752862811\" width=606 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/f38a047e6ad501dd91e62f9109678412.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/f38a047e6ad501dd91e62f9109678412.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/f38a047e6ad501dd91e62f9109678412.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>平原、深洞、森林、冰川...你可以探索这片大陆上的每一个角落，等待你的不仅有尘封的宝藏，也可能是强大的怪物。打败它们，守护这个世界吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/30d97a066c5ee79deda9a57bac1c564d.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=107 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/679f09a933ff732337b5f7eaf7f9880e.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/679f09a933ff732337b5f7eaf7f9880e.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/679f09a933ff732337b5f7eaf7f9880e.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在游戏中，你还可以化身飞龙，通过飞行探索陆地无法到达的区域。同时，飞龙形态下还有一整套的全新技能等待你来体验！",
